{
  "stem": "22237.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We were not well to do, but we were very happy.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Sometimes there was one bar of chocolate in the middle of the table, and everybody had a piece of chocolate, and that meant an awful lot.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "We were all happy with a small piece of chocolate.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Passover was a big holiday, yes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I remember my mother would make a certain wine from raisins, a raisin wine.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She would call it [GERMAN] wine in Germany.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we all drank from that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we enjoyed Passover, just like all the other holidays.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But it was something special because as-- even today, it's very special, because we eat matzoh instead of bread.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, now we are talking about-- Hitler came on power in 1933.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I started school in 1926.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "School was-- I used to go to a school called Philantropin, P-H-I-L-A-N-T-R-O-P-I-N.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "All of five-- all of us five children used to visit that school, Philantropin.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Philantropin was a Jewish school.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Not a yeshiva, a Jewish school that was very well-known all over Germany.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It-- Jewish students came from everywhere.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And it-- we visited-- all of us visited that school.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And actually, we all liked going to school, my oldest sister especially.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "She was kind of a genius.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "She was very bright, and she jumped classes many times.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And the teachers were very-- whenever they heard an Ebe would come to the Philantropin, they were thrilled because they thought we were all going to be as smart as my oldest sister.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But none of us was as smart.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] She was very special.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I liked going to school until Hitler came on power.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Then it was hard.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In-- it was hard in  a way that-- when-- the minute Hitler came in power, it was hard-- everything got much harder.",
      "word_count": 22
    }
  ],
